{"tid":1853881,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"下星期有機會大升嘅肺炎概念股預測","createTime":"2020-01-31T08:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T01:08:30.000Z","uid":14348,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4152decb27c61b35734488e88ff04eac281f9b7","tid":1853881,"uid":14348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:11:34.000Z","msg":"1）1345 中國先鋒醫藥， 係，呢個真係炒，其他炒爛曬，呢隻個升勢岩岩先起，下星期應該會做呢隻<br />\n<br />\n2）1672 歌禮製藥。呢隻貨真價實，佢隻藥俾中國政府拎來試用過有效，不過隻藥就未批出市面嘅，但琴日就有個副省長參觀過佢地間廠，大力支持仲話要特事特辦開綠色通道。加上睇返佢發行價，呢隻嘅穩陣度值得小炒。<br />\n<br />\n3）8225 中國醫療集團。雖然已經散左水，不過見收市競價收高，有機會再炒返起，不過危險率高。雖則係咁，回報可能都會高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸：憑感覺估計，大家一齊研究下"},{"pid":"4b9d48dee314ce71aff00642c77ba33fdecd936f","tid":1853881,"uid":100819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"1672,唯一有藥嘅股。"},{"pid":"1877c87f4250e4c5b8510aa766073e1114be447f","tid":1853881,"uid":138050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:20:31.000Z","msg":"1345 一入跌到仆街<br />\n蝕左$3000"},{"pid":"9cbe824b83f7fc142f7f7dd6160b6fe4b319da7a","tid":1853881,"uid":14348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b9d48dee314ce71aff00642c77ba33fdecd936f","tid":1853881,"uid":100819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"1672,唯一有藥嘅股。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"雖然隻藥未批，不過中國特事特辦，真係有效的話批左一定有唔錯嘅升幅"},{"pid":"1faa49804d3737827fa0f20c66d6e93dedbe0c53","tid":1853881,"uid":14348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1877c87f4250e4c5b8510aa766073e1114be447f","tid":1853881,"uid":138050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:20:31.000Z","msg":"1345 一入跌到仆街<br />\n蝕左$3000"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:21:31.000Z","msg":"你咩位入"},{"pid":"46a164745b8adf0f1827abd00b8ddb2414579e21","tid":1853881,"uid":138050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1faa49804d3737827fa0f20c66d6e93dedbe0c53","tid":1853881,"uid":14348,"like":0,